Noteworthy changes since SQLWork 3.0
====================================

Multiple connections are now supported, each with its own work area.

Support for multiple databases has been added. In this release SQLWork now
supports mySQL databases as well as Oracle.

Access to often used queries is available via a "bookmarks" mechanism.

Any number of connections may be remembered and automatically opened when
SQLWork is started

Query plans may be displayed.

Query results may be sorted by any column

SQL Scripts are supported.


